description: This file defines a mock class `SecureStorageServiceMock` for the `SecureStorageService` gRPC service, using Google Mock (`gmock`) to facilitate unit testing. It includes mock methods for the service's RPC calls like `GetValue`, `UpdateValue`, `DeleteValue`, `DeleteAllValues`, and `SeedValue`. The class inherits from the generated gRPC service class and overrides these methods.

classes.name: SecureStorageServiceMock
classes.description: A mock class for the SecureStorageService gRPC service, providing mock implementations for RPC calls to facilitate unit testing.

methods.name: GetValue
methods.description: Mock method for the GetValue RPC, simulating retrieval of a value from secure storage.

methods.name: UpdateValue
methods.description: Mock method for the UpdateValue RPC, simulating updating a value in secure storage.

methods.name: DeleteValue
methods.description: Mock method for the DeleteValue RPC, simulating deletion of a specific value from secure storage.

methods.name: DeleteAllValues
methods.description: Mock method for the DeleteAllValues RPC, simulating deletion of all values from secure storage.

methods.name: SeedValue
methods.description: Mock method for the SeedValue RPC, simulating seed data operation in secure storage.
